test.sh:
    shell script that does a simple smoke-test on lab0
    
    test cases:
        check if input content is the same as output content:
            neither input file or output file specified
            only input file specified
            only output file specified
            both input and output file specified
        check if exit code is correct:
            exit with 0 for the 4 cases above
            exit with 1 when unrecognized argument given
            exit with 2 when unable to open input file
            exit with 3 when unable to open output file
            exit with 4 when caught and received SIGSEGV

lab0.c:
    C source file for lab0
backtrace.png:
    screenshot showing a segfault and associated stack-trace in gdb
breakpoint.png:
    screenshot showing a breakpoint and variable inspection in gdb
Makefile:
    the makefile to build the program and the tarball
README:
    identification information, description of the included files and 
    the smoke-test cases in the check target